== Baruk achem Pustok ==
'''Book of Baruch'''



Hem pustok Hebrev Povitr Pustokant mellona. Greg Povitr Pustokant tem Jeremias ani Vilap hance modem ghatlam.  Prostavna (1/1-14) pormannem hem pustok Barukan,  Babilonient boroilolem.  Baruk, Jeremiasacho chittnis aslo.  Tantunt : opradh mandun gheun kelolem magnnem ani bhorvanso asa (1/15- 3/8);  ‘Zannvaiechi’ kovita asa ( 3/9 -4/4).  He kovitent zannavai somurtik sor kelea; ek provadik utaro (4/5-5/9) asa zantunt Jerusalem pordes bhogtoleam-xim uloita ani Baruk provadi fuddaracho bhorvanso diun tika bhuzvonn dita.  

Prostavna,  Greg bhaxentlean boroiloli, Magnnem 1/15-3/8 dubav nastana Hebrev bhaxen boroilolem.  Sovea ovesvorant asa tem Jeremiasachem potr murti puza kortat tancher add asam.  Hea potrantle thodde vixoi Iz. 44/9-20 ani Jer. 10/1-16 hantunt melltat.

Hem Pustok Judev porza ximpddon poddloli tedna aplem dhormik jivit samballunk tannim kosle upai ghetle tea vixim mhotvachi mhaiti dita.  Toxench, Jerusalea-xim sombond, magnnem, somurtik visvaxiponn, prachit korpachem mon, fuddaracho bhorvanso he-I vixoi asat. 











